OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPaul Rusesabagina: From    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FHotel Rwanda hero to       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fconvicted terrorist        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Paul Rusesabagina, the subject of      
OL,6, Oscar-nominated film Hotel Rwanda      
OL,7, portraying his life-saving actions     
OL,8, during the Rwandan genocide, is now    
OL,9, facing many years in prison for        
OL,10, terror-related crimes.                 
OL,12,FNearly two decades ago he presented    
OL,13,Fhimself as an ordinary man who happened
OL,14,Fto be caught up in extraordinary times.
OL,16,FThe Rwandan former hotel manager, 67,  
OL,17,Fis credited with saving the lives of   
OL,18,Fmore than 1,000 people during the      
OL,19,Fgenocide.                              
